snippet.title: Aeronautica Imperialis: Flight Command - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Command the burning skies of the 41st millennium with Aeronautica Imperialis: Flight Command.

Available 28th May 2020. Wishlist on Steam now https://store.steampowered.com/app/610160/Aeronautica_Imperialis_Flight_Command/

Join the conversation at:
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/NbDdVzh
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/flight_command  
Website: https://www.aeronauticaimperialisflightcommand.com/

See you in the skies, Commander!
